title: Michael W Smith A New Hallelujah The Live Worship DVD
description:
Join Michael W. Smith, 12,000 worshippers and a 250-voice choir for one powerfull night of worship. Experience the electricity of the mood, the moving music, and insights from one of Christian music's most-loved recording artists and worship leaders as he guides hearts into passionate praise. A NEW HALLELUJAH - THE LIVE WORSHIP DVD features all of the songs from A NEW HALLELUJAH CD, plus four new tracks & behing-the-scenes footage.

- Prepare Ye The Way
- A New Hallelujah [With The African Children's Choir]
- When I Think Of You [With The African Children's Choir]
- Mighty To Save
- Shout Unto God
- Amazing Grace (My Chains Are Gone)
- Deep In Love With You
- Healing Rain / Let It Rain
- Majesty
- I Surrender all [With Special Guest Coalo Zamorano]
- Oh Draw Me Lord (Draw me Near)
- Grace
- Help Is On The Way [With Special Guest Israel Houghton]
- The River Is Rising
- Love In His Right Hand
- Siwano [Ft. The African Childrens Choir]
- A New Hallelujah (Reprise)

BONUS:
- BTS: A New Hallelujah
- 4 New Tracks From The Live Concert Event
- 5.1 Surround Sound
